  <description><![CDATA[<p>Residence Les Chalets de Layssia makes for the perfect escape in the beautiful village of Samoëns. You’re a short walk from the village centre which is situated in a valley with beautiful mountain surroundings. The property is made up of self-catered apartments, some of which can sleep up to ten people. With an indoor swimming pool, sauna and hammam on site, this is the perfect base to explore Samoëns and the surrounding area.</p>]]></description>
