  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Two to four person apartments</strong> are approx. 35m². There is one bedroom with a double bed or twin beds (please specify preference when booking). There is also a small lounge area with a sofa bed.</p>
<p><strong>Four to six person apartments</strong> are approx. 50m². There is one double bedroom and one twin bedroom. There is also a small lounge area with a sofa bed.</p>
<p><strong>Six to eight person apartments</strong> are approx. 70m². There is one double bedroom and two twin bedrooms. There is also a small lounge area with a sofa bed.</p>
<p><strong>Eight to ten person cabin apartments</strong> are approx. 85m². There are three double/twin bedrooms, a lounge area with sofa bed and a cabin room with bunk beds (bunk beds are suitable for children over 6 years up to 14 years). This apartment type is available on request only, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Eight to ten person duplex apartments</strong> are approx. 85m². There are four double/twin bedrooms. There is also a small lounge area with a sofa bed. This apartment type is available on request only, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>All apartments have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Well-equipped kitchenettes</li>
<li>Balcony/terrace</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
</ul>
<p>High chair and cot available on request (max. one cot per unit).</p>
<p><strong>General information</strong></p>
<p>Check in: <strong>5pm</strong></p>
<p>Check out: <strong>10am</strong></p>
<p><strong>Local fees and taxes</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>There is a deposit of €400 payable on arrival.</li>
<li>There is a resort tax of approx. €1.20 per person, per day payable locally (under 18s free of charge).</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
